The food was awesome.	The gravy was ok.	The mulligatawny is OK.	The naan bread is amazing.	The customer service is excellent!	The environment is pretty sterile.	Nice portions.	The FOOD was great!	It's a Byob place.	The vegetable korma was good.	The worst was the lamb chop.	The mango lassi is OK.	The CTM itself was horrible.	Very good food and service.	The host was gregarious and funny.	The channai and naans are great.	Samosas are fun.	The service was slow but attentive.	The rice was excellent - as well cooked basmati can be.	The decor was quite nice.